# Walkthrough: ai-doc Integracija sa Trinity Protocol-om

## Šta je urađeno

### 1. Workspace Inicijalizacija
Pokrenuto `ai-doc init` — kreirana `.ai-workspace/` struktura:
```
.ai-workspace/
├── personas/       ← Trinity persona
├── tasks/active/   ← 3 aktivna takmičenja
├── tasks/completed/
├── rules/project/  ← Trinity pravila
├── cache/compiled/ ← Kompajlovani kontekst za IDE
└── analysis/
```

### 2. Trinity Persona
Kreiran [.ai-workspace/personas/trinity.json](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/kaggle-arena/.ai-workspace/personas/trinity.json):
- Uloga: Kaggle Grand Master ML Engineer
- Framework: 3-6-2 Dialectic
- Guardrails: JudgeGuard v2.1, ProcessGuard, 7-Gate Submit

### 3. Registrovana Takmičenja kao Tasks
| Task ID | Naziv | Status |
|---|---|---|
| task-001 | Spaceship Titanic — Calibration (OOF 0.8125) | 🔥 ACTIVE |
| task-002 | WiDS 2026 — Survival Analysis C-Index | 🔥 ACTIVE |
| task-003 | AIMO 2026 — Math Olympiad Solver | 🔥 ACTIVE |

### 4. ai-doc build Kompajlovanje
`ai-doc build` automatski propagovao Trinity pravila u:
- [.google/instructions.md](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/kaggle-arena/.google/instructions.md) ← **Gemini** odmah čita
- [.claude/instructions.md](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/kaggle-arena/.claude/instructions.md) ← Claude
- `.cursorrules` ← Cursor IDE
- `.windsurfrules` ← Windsurf
- [.github/copilot-instructions.md](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/kaggle-arena/.github/copilot-instructions.md) ← GitHub Copilot

### 5. Makefile Proširenje
```bash
make ai-status    # kombinuje ai-doc + JudgeGuard status
make ai-task      # lista svih Trinity tasks
make ai-ritual    # auto-evolucija + kernel + build
make ai-sync      # build + evolve
make ai-kernel    # kernel navigacija
make ai-prompt COMP=spaceship-titanic  # kontekstualni prompt
```

### 6. Novi Workflow
[.agent/workflows/aidoc_sync.md](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/kaggle-arena/.agent/workflows/aidoc_sync.md) — `/aidoc_sync` slash komanda za ritual sinhronizacije.

## Validacija

```
✅ ai-doc status → "AI CLI v2.0 Refactored"  
✅ ai-doc task list → 3 tasks prikazana  
✅ make ai-status → ai-doc + JudgeGuard u jednom prikazu  
✅ ai-doc build → dokumentacija validirana, bez placeholder-a  
```
